  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-customer-story=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-start gap-6 flex-initial article-module__XJFYTq__content\">\n   <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-between flex-initial w-full gap-4 pt-2\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-row items-center justify-start gap-1.5 flex-initial\">\n     <p class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900\">1<!-- --> min <!-- -->read</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6 flex-1 justify-start\"></div>\n    <time class=\"text-copy-14 text-gray-900 order-2 md:order-3\" datetime=\"2026-04-09T08:00-07:00\">Apr 9, 2026</time>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"rounded-md p-2 bg-background-100 shadow-sm bg-clip-padding max-w-[900px] grid grid-cols-1 sm:border-l-0 sm:border-r-0 sm:rounded-none sm:border-[var(--guide-color)] sm:max-w-none sm:w-full mt-4 mb-6 max-w-[var(--article-max-width)]\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"900\" height=\"471\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic rounded-sm border border-solid border-gray-200 image-module__ssnYEW__lightMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3e2JFwro5V3WuQddGxlfeA%2F5934a67ae44ec05fa73b14505a555f3c%2FVercel_Django_Light.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3e2JFwro5V3WuQddGxlfeA%2F5934a67ae44ec05fa73b14505a555f3c%2FVercel_Django_Light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F3e2JFwro5V3WuQddGxlfeA%2F5934a67ae44ec05fa73b14505a555f3c%2FVercel_Django_Light.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"><img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" width=\"900\" height=\"471\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image-module__ssnYEW__intrinsic rounded-sm border border-solid border-gray-200 image-module__ssnYEW__darkMode\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40ebnMJ8rvYYCUHJ21I8vs%2F16c507c06355068c0f95fdb643fff2d4%2FVercel_Django_Dark.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1x, https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40ebnMJ8rvYYCUHJ21I8vs%2F16c507c06355068c0f95fdb643fff2d4%2FVercel_Django_Dark.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"https://vercel.com/vc-ap-vercel-marketing/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.vercel.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fcontentful%2Fimage%2Fe5382hct74si%2F40ebnMJ8rvYYCUHJ21I8vs%2F16c507c06355068c0f95fdb643fff2d4%2FVercel_Django_Dark.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\">\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"><a href=\"https://www.djangoproject.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://www.djangoproject.com/\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Django</a>, one of the most popular high-level <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/runtimes/python\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/functions/runtimes/python\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Python</a> web frameworks, for rapid development, is now supported with zero-configuration. You can now instantly deploy Django full-stack apps or APIs on Vercel.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Vercel now recognizes and deeply understands the specifications of Django applications, removing the need for redirects in <code>vercel.json</code> or using the <code>/api</code> folder.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">All applications on Vercel use <a href=\"https://vercel.com/fluid\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/fluid\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Fluid compute</a> with <a target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/blog/introducing-active-cpu-pricing-for-fluid-compute\" data-zone=\"same\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\" href=\"https://vercel.com/blog/introducing-active-cpu-pricing-for-fluid-compute\">Active CPU pricing</a> by default. Static files will be served by the <a href=\"https://vercel.com/cdn\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/cdn\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Vercel CDN</a>.</p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Deploy <a href=\"https://vercel.com/templates/python/django-notes\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/templates/python/django-notes\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">Django on Vercel</a> or visit the Django on Vercel <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/frameworks/backend/django\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-track=\"true\" data-track-click-name=\"article_link\" data-track-click-value=\"https://vercel.com/docs/frameworks/backend/django\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link-module__Q1NRQq__link no-underline link-module__Q1NRQq__highlight [&amp;_u]:no-underline\">documentation</a></p>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\"></p>\n   <h3 class=\"text-heading-20 lg:text-heading-24 font-semibold relative group w-full pt-8 text-module__qZtYrq__subheading\"><a class=\"flex items-center justify-center flex-col absolute left-0 bottom-0 mt-auto mb-auto w-8 h-8 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 -translate-x-3/4 group-hover:-translate-x-full delay-75 duration-300 transition-all text-gray-900 hover:text-gray-1000 hover:scale-110 focus-visible:-translate-x-full focus-visible:opacity-100 top-6 [#changelog-description_&amp;]:hidden\" href=\"#example-django-app\" id=\"example-django-app\" style=\"scroll-margin-top:90px\"> \n     <svg data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\" />\n     </svg> \n     <span class=\"sr-only\">Link to heading</span> \n    </a>Example Django app</h3>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">CLI entry point</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hasFileName code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__header\">\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__fileName\">\n       <span class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__filenameP\">manage.py</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__actions\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-python code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> os</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> sys</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">os</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">environ</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">setdefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"app.settings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> django</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">core</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">management </span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> execute_from_command_line</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L7\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C1c3d18ce-L8\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">execute_from_command_line</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token plain\">sys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">argv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">Project settings</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hasFileName code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__header\">\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__fileName\">\n       <span class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__filenameP\">app/settings.py</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__actions\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-python code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">SECRET_KEY </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"my-secret-key\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">DEBUG </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token boolean\">False</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">ALLOWED_HOSTS </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"localhost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"127.0.0.1\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\".vercel.app\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L4\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">ROOT_URLCONF </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"app.urls\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L5\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">WSGI_APPLICATION </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token string\">\"app.wsgi.application\"</span><span class=\"token plain\"></span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C671feb3a-L6\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\">INSTALLED_APPS </span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token plain\"> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"app\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></div></div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"text-center text-copy-14 text-gray-900\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text-copy-16 lg:text-copy-18 text-module__qZtYrq__paragraph\">URL routing table</p>\n   <div class=\"flex flex-col items-stretch justify-start gap-4 flex-initial blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"relative code-block-module__NOThwW__wrapper code-block-module__NOThwW__hasFileName code-block-module__NOThwW__hideLineNumbers blog-code-block-module__TEKDOa__codeBlock\" data-geist-code-block=\"\">\n     <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__header\">\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__fileName\">\n       <span class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__filenameP\">app/urls.py</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__actions\">\n       <button aria-label=\"Copy code\" class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__copyButton\" type=\"button\"></button>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <pre class=\"prism-code language-python code-block-module__NOThwW__pre\"><code class=\"code-block-module__NOThwW__code\" data-geist-code-block=\"true\"><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C30f97d65-L1\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> django</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">urls </span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> path</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C30f97d65-L2\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\"></span><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span><span class=\"token plain\"> app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token plain\">views </span><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token plain\"> index</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C30f97d65-L3\" style=\"font-feature-settings:&quot;liga&quot; off\"><div class=\"token-line\"><span class=\"token plain\" style=\"display:inline-block\">\n</span></div></div><div class=\"line\" data-geist-code-block-line=\"true\" id=\"C30f97d65-L4\" style=\"font-feature-se